t = int(input())
for i in range(t):
    l = list(map(str, input().split()))
    (d, e) = map(str, input().split())
    x = l.index(d)
    y = l.index(e)
    print(l[min(x, y)])

T = int(input())
for _ in range(T):
    com = list(map(str, input().split()))
    (x, y) = map(str, input().split())
    print(x) if com.index(x) < com.index(y) else print(y)

for i in range(int(input())):
    l = input().split()
    (x, y) = input().split()
    a = l.index(x)
    b = l.index(y)
    m = min(a, b)
    print(l[m])
